  "title": "Workplace Safety and Health Officer @ Clementi",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Workplace Safety Health Officer for LTA tunnels construction</strong></u></p><p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><p>· Preparation and implementation of Safety Program</p><p>· Ensure all work practices comply with company safety policy and WSH act</p><p>· Advise on work plan / Risk Assessment / safe work procedures</p><p>· Ability to identify problems and provide solutions</p><p>· Able to lead fellow colleagues and inculcate them towards safe work culture</p><p>· Compile all relevant report and records, carry out daily safety inspection</p><p>· Prepare and submit weekly safety report as required by management and clients</p><p>· Other ad-hoc duties assigned by the Project Manager</p><p>· Have experience in confined space, high-altitude work, civil engineering or electrical engineering projects</p><p><br /><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>· Must be a Singapore Registered Safety Officer / Workplace Safety & Health Officer with Ministry of Manpower (Singapore)</p><p>· Must have professional knowledge in WSHE legislation and regulations (WSH act and Environment)</p><p>· Must have Workplace Safety & Health Diploma</p><p>· Min. Diploma in Building / Civil / Structural Engineering</p><p>· Min. 5 years of WSHO experience in LTA tunnelling</p><p>· Physically fit and healthy, hardworking and driven</p><p>· Remuneration will commensurate with experience and qualifications</p><p>· Candidates who are able to come on board within 2 weeks after job offer will have an added advantage</p>",
